high_descs: turn to the right and go to the center of the counter top and face the counter top
pick up the dirty rag on the right that is in front of the candle stick
turn right and go across the room to the left side of the sink
put the dirty rag in the sink, turn on the water to rinse it off and pick it back up
turn around and go across the room to the white dresser on the left that is to the right of the toilet
open the bottom drawer of the dresser, place rag inside dresser and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: put a clean rag in a bottom dresser drawer

high_descs: Pick up the dirty towel to the right.
Turn around and head towards the sink.
Place the towel in the sink, turn on the faucet, wash the towel, turn off the faucet, and pick up the towel.
Turn right towards the white dresser on your left.
Open the bottom drawer and place the towel inside.
anns.task_desc: Clean the dirty towel to place inside the dresser.

high_descs: Move to the white counter on the left.

Bring the rag to the sink.

anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned rag in the bottom drawer.
